
Description:

Add support for the PROXY protocol.

https://github.com/haproxy/haproxy/blob/master/doc/proxy-protocol.txt


Config changes:

None.


Upgrade instructions:

To enable support for the PROXY protocol in imapd, pop3d, nntpd, httpd, or
timesieved, add the 'P' command line option to the service in cyrus.conf.


